<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Volley Vibes</title>

    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffb6c1, #add8e6);
            color: #333;
        }

        header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        nav a {
            margin: 0 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #333;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: #ff4da6;
        }

        .hero {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 80px 20px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 40px;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            width: 80%;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<header>
    <div class="logo">🏐 Volley Vibes</div>
    <nav>
        <a href="#home">Home</a>
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#how">How It Works</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
</header>
<section class="hero" id="home">
    <h1>Welcome to Volley Vibes 💙💖</h1>
    <p>Your friendly volleyball club for beginners & advanced players</p>
</section>
<section class="card" id="about">
    <h2>About Our Club</h2>
    <p>
        Volley Vibes is a fun, inclusive volleyball club where everyone can learn,
        improve, and enjoy the game. We focus on teamwork, skills, and confidence.
    </p>
</section>
<section class="card" id="how">
    <h2>How It Works</h2>
    <p>
        We run weekly training sessions, skill drills, and friendly matches.
        Players are grouped by skill level so everyone can improve at their own pace.
    </p>
</section>
<section class="card" id="contact">
    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>Email: gracematewai@gmail.com</p>
    <p>Phone: 0438 915 312</p>
    <p>Location: Rouse Hill, NSW, Australia</p>
</section>
<footer>
    <p>© 2026 Volley Vibes</p>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
